			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「应战对策」充能总值<span color="#ffdfbf">180</span><span>，角色进入「夜魂加持」状态时，每次积攒</span><span color="#99ff99">30</span><span>充能；角色维持「夜魂加持」状态时，每秒积攒</span><span color="#99ff99">10</span><span>充能。充能填满后转换攻击方式。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1018" width="483" height="39" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
