			<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/驱侵之役-秘源机兵统御械%B7毁灭武装.assets/Image_21.png')" x="128" y="560" blendMode="normal">
			</BitmapImage>
		</Group>
		<RichText x="66" y="640" width="462" height="58" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#bfffbf">(N4) <span color="#ffffff">抗性：入战前</span><span color="#ffdfbf">310%</span><span color="#ffffff">，入场</span><span color="#ffdfbf">280%</span><span color="#ffffff">，荡除</span><span color="#ffdfbf">210%</span><span color="#ffffff">，夜魂</span><span color="#ffdfbf">50%</span><span color="#ffffff">，<br/>凝滞</span><span color="#99ffff">冰-40%</span><span color="#ffffff">/其他</span><span color="#ffdfbf">0%</span><span color="#ffffff">。若期间</span><span color="#ffdfbf">未进入过「凝滞」或「夜魂」状态</span><span color="#ffffff">，<br/></span><span color="#dfdfdf">则</span><span color="#ffffff">退出荡除模式时，全抗将升至</span><span color="#ffdfbf">80%</span><span color="#ffffff">。</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(N5) </span><span color="#ffffff">入场时短时间</span><span color="#ffdfbf">380%</span><span color="#ffffff">。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/驱侵之役-秘源机兵统御械%B7毁灭武装.assets/Image_22.png')" x="1396" y="267" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1538" y="320" width="443" height="130" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="18" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">处于「应战对策」状态时，其将产生2个高速强追踪玩家的泉眼，移至玩家处立即生成水柱，高频造成<span color="#7fbfff">45%</span><span>伤害；「液流动量」越多，泉眼移速越快。<br/>该模式下，仍会累积「动量」，将其打空仍可进入「凝滞」；同样，在「动量」</span><span color="#ffdfbf">&lt;7.4%</span><span>(10) 时，不会进入「应战对策」状态。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/驱侵之役-秘源机兵统御械%B7毁灭武装.assets/Image_23.png')" x="1396" y="523" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1538" y="576" width="438" height="259" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="18" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「<span textDecoration="underline">液流动量</span><span>」初始拥有一定值，随时间持续增长，受到</span><span color="#99ffff">冰元素</span><span>攻击后会回退；当动量积蓄至不同进度时，所产生的效果不同：<br/>当「动量」累积至<br/></span><span color="#ffdfbf">&lt;7.4%</span><span>(10) / </span><span color="#ffdfbf">7.4%</span><span>(10) / </span><span color="#ffdfbf">22.2%</span><span>(30)</span><span color="#ffdfbf"> </span><span>/ </span><span color="#ffdfbf">44.4%</span><span>(60) / </span><span fontFamily="SDK_TW_Web" color="#ffdfbf">≥</span><span color="#ffdfbf">88.9%</span><span>(120) 时，统御械将：<br/></span><span color="#bfffbf">减抗</span><span>并「凝滞」 / </span><span color="#ffbfbf">加抗</span><span>并开始喷水 / 水柱伤害提升至50% / 水柱伤害提升至100% / 额外产生2枚水柱，同时水龙头转速随着阶段进行不断增加；<br/>「凝滞」状态下，统御械停止攻击，所有抗性大幅降低，</span><span color="#99ffff">冰抗</span><span>额外降低；「动量」高于10时退出该状态。<br/></span><span color="#ffbfbf">(N5)</span><span> 首次进入凝滞状态时角色恢复</span><span color="#ffdfbf">36</span><span>元素能量。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/驱侵之役-秘源机兵统御械%B7毁灭武装.assets/Image_24.png')" x="1520" y="490">
		</BitmapImage>
